{"tid":1581184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 連登仔又中計！警狗想拖曬所有紀律部隊同其他政府部門落水！","createTime":"2019-09-19T12:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T06:31:15.000Z","uid":259898,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bc03c79f25786c7ab02ab6ec82d25a7f9e2e2674","tid":1581184,"uid":259898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n突然間今日成個熱門有大量post都係討論其他部門點樣同警犬合作<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>企圖拖曬其他政府部門落水 轉移視線等市民唔再剩係針對警犬</strong></span><br />\n佢地分化字眼: 消防狗/消防警狗連成一線/<br />\nxxxx一家親/所有政府部門都係狗<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">等你地針對埋消防救護入境海關醫護人員<br />\n佢地就唔洗俾人isolate</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n引用另一位巴打既post<br />\n消防員係唔係朋友？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555336</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">撐佢地一個原因就夠。<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">孤立警隊</span></span>。<br />\n你知唔知每次我地向消防員同救護員歡呼？<br />\n警察心入面幾難受？<br />\n見到消防同救護，就一定盡全力歡呼。<br />\n比d警察睇到自己係同消防幾大對比。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至於政府部門高層一定撐政府是常識吧<br />\n佢唔奶共佢點上到呢個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再幻想邊個部門可以反黑警<br />\n重點係好多前線手足都係同路人 真正執行order做野既係佢地 佢地係職位上面幫到盡唔通又要高調講出黎博炒咩<br />\n藍屍點都有 但任何公司都會有藍有黃<br />\n佢地跟例做野就夠 唔好俾黑警轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">各有各做 不分化唔係口號啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完出去推返有用行動post上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b8c5dfd49e0833ac5bfc9eed40b7b730a6bc85","tid":1581184,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:24:52.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=652b8619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"24c7caedf344ee9dc76eb1b49c5acd33ea775d71","tid":1581184,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=ff866db9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=ca5220df\" target=\"_bl